snippet.title: A-Train (Amiga 50Hz) - Intro
snippet.description:
Music by Brad Madix, Matt Nathan and Russell Lieblich

A-Train for the Commodore Amiga (c) 1992 by The Dreamers Guild / Maxis / Ocean
Based on the NEC PC-98 / FM-Towns release titled Take the A-Train III (c) 1990 by Artdink
